description:
  The paper deals with the existence and uniqueness of the solution of the
backward stochastic variational inequality: \begin{equation}
\left\{\begin{array} {l}-dY_{t}+\partial \varphi(Y_{t})dt \ni
F(t,Y_{t},Z_{t})dt-Z_{t}dB_{t},\;0\leq t<T \\ Y_{T}=\eta, \end{array}
\right.\end{equation} where $F$ satisfies a local boundedness condition.

Comment: 6 pages, misprints corrected, reference list updated, MSC added;
  presented at the XXXII Int. Congress of the Italian Society of Historians of
  Physics and Astronomy (SISFA), Rome 2012

Comment: 32 pages, 10 figures; Int. Math. Res. Notices (2015); SAGE worksheet
  available at http://sashakolpakov.wordpress.com/research/list-of-papers/;
  typo on page 28, line -4 of the published version corrected

Comment: This version corrects some errors from the previous version;
  generalizes the potential-theoretic setting; incorporates a title change; and
  adds an additional co-author

Comment: PhD thesis, Humboldt-Universit\"at zu Berlin;
  urn:nbn:de:kobv:11-100232371;
  http://edoc.hu-berlin.de/docviews/abstract.php?id=42042
